# 高德 iOS SDK 静态 framework 目录
# 下载链接: https://lbs.amap.com/api/ios-sdk/download
# 需要下载 2 个 SDK:
#   1. 3D 地图 SDK (AMap3DMap)
#   2. 基础 SDK (AMapFoundation)
# 完整目录结构:
#   Vendor/AMap/AMap3DMap.framework
#   Vendor/AMap/AMapFoundation.framework
#   Vendor/AMap/AMapSearch.framework   (可选, Sprint 1 不需要)
#   Vendor/AMap/AMapLocation.framework  (可选, Sprint 1 不需要)
